{"tid":2369223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑狗又贏]四川漢心情差扯下國旗踩踏判囚10個月","createTime":"2021-01-17T03:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T05:02:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f73a7edf440e43bab71ff026a35904034f16f6b","tid":2369223,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:11:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">投錯胎，黑狗咁踢都無事呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JydD1Tk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJydD1Tk.gif&h=fa48161d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20210117/s00004/1610845383100/%e5%9b%9b%e5%b7%9d%e6%bc%a2%e5%bf%83%e6%83%85%e5%b7%ae%e6%89%af%e4%b8%8b%e5%9c%8b%e6%97%97%e8%b8%a9%e8%b8%8f%e5%88%a4%e5%9b%9a10%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20210117%2Fs00004%2F1610845383100%2F%25e5%259b%259b%25e5%25b7%259d%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e5%25bf%2583%25e6%2583%2585%25e5%25b7%25ae%25e6%2589%25af%25e4%25b8%258b%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%2597%2597%25e8%25b8%25a9%25e8%25b8%258f%25e5%2588%25a4%25e5%259b%259a10%25e5%2580%258b%25e6%259c%2588&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=dfcc6fe6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20210117%2Fs00004%2F1610845383100%2F%25e5%259b%259b%25e5%25b7%259d%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e5%25bf%2583%25e6%2583%2585%25e5%25b7%25ae%25e6%2589%25af%25e4%25b8%258b%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%2597%2597%25e8%25b8%25a9%25e8%25b8%258f%25e5%2588%25a4%25e5%259b%259a10%25e5%2580%258b%25e6%259c%2588&h=ee7b0468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20210117/s00004/1610845383100/%e5%9b%9b%e5%b7%9d%e6%bc%a2%e5%bf%83%e6%83%85%e5%b7%ae%e6%89%af%e4%b8%8b%e5%9c%8b%e6%97%97%e8%b8%a9%e8%b8%8f%e5%88%a4%e5%9b%9a10%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88</a><br />\n<br />\n中國庭審公開網近日公布一宗侮辱國旗案件，四川省夾江縣居民吳某因為踩踏國旗，被判處有期徒刑10個月。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，去年10月5日上午7時許，吳某在上班途中路過夾江縣一家KTV時，突然跳起來將懸掛在路邊的國旗扯下踩踏，隨後帶着國旗揚長而去。有關視頻在微信群、朋友圈廣傳。警方翌日在吳某家中將其抓獲。吳某如實供述自己所犯罪行，並自願簽署認罪認罰具結書。據吳某交代，踩踏國旗是因為心情不好，當時腦子發熱才做出那樣的舉動。<br />\n<br />\n案件今年1月13日開審，吳某當庭認罪，但對量刑10個月有異議，認為太重，稱「要麼判決半年，要麼判決死刑，活着太沒有意義」，但在宣判後表示不上訴。"},{"pid":"e58189effe157e815c8092817529b4705b98b695","tid":2369223,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T05:02:09.000Z","msg":"黑狗: Join US"}]}